{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>TOTAL RELOAD</strong> you have to learn to \u201cthink with wires\u201d or, in other words, understand that by temporarily supplying power to various objects you can get to previously inaccessible locations. It is difficult to feel the full depth of this game mechanics from a video, so we released a demo that contains 20% of the locations from the full version of the game. In the demo version, you will be able to fully experience what it means to \u201cthink with wires\u201d and learn how to interact with some devices: Quantum Transporters, Energy Transmitters, Sensor Grids, Energy Cubes, Energy Converters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will be able to start playing the full game from where you finish playing the demo. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/extras/Energy_Transmitter_-_GIF_-_480_x_270.gif?t=1732732754\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/extras/Two-Phase_Energy_Transmitter_-_GIF_-_480_x_270.gif?t=1732732754\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/extras/TOTAL_RELOAD_05.gif?t=1732732754\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"LEFT REVIEW","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3135100/2cc7be671e32fe347a747c217f23efaa45108cfb.jpg"},{"name":"WISHLISTED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3135100/08e92f19799d97e258614361b899e231afeaf445.jpg"}],"total":2},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732732754","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps